summary: Selene Void is a level 62 Ashen Race Character with a mix of wood elf
descriptionHtml:
She was mostly made to be a destruction mage character but then i decided to make her a good archer and one handed sword Character.
<br />The main Quest is not complete
<br />Dawnguard is complete with the vampire side but later I cured her and somehow she still has Vampire lord power
<br />Dark brotherhood quest is complete/ and so is Theives Guild 
<br />she has over 50k of gold on her
<br />Breeze house was purchased
<br />
